		as.person("G Carnevale"),
		as.person("LJ Harmon")),
	journal = "Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America",
  	year = "2009",
	volume = "106",
	pages = "13410-13414",

        textVersion = "Alfaro Michael E, Francesco Santini, Chad Brock, Hugo Alamillo, Alex Dornburg, Daniel L Rabosky, Giorgio Carnevale, and Luke J Harmon. 2009. Nine exceptional radiations plus high turnover explain species diversity in jawed vertebrates. PNAS 106:13410-13414.")

